01:25:14,957 --> 01:25:17,321
Also, while we're under suspension, we have Ms.

499
01:25:17,381 --> 01:25:28,800
Melanie McLaughlin and Angela Munsell-Moore regarding family and community engagement, a status update on the investigation, and the successful plan for superintendent and deputy superintendent.

500
01:25:38,323 --> 01:25:41,728
Hello school committee members, Madam Mayor, community.

501
01:25:42,129 --> 01:25:46,375
My name is Melanie Perkins McLaughlin and I live on Alston Street in Medford.

