580
01:31:29,911 --> 01:31:33,413
And again, none of this is personal for me around Mr. Bellson.

581
01:31:33,493 --> 01:31:38,516
We've had everybody knows we've had our differences, Mr. Bellson, but we've always been very professional and respectful with each other.

582
01:31:38,536 --> 01:31:40,977
It's never been personal and it never will be.

583
01:31:42,158 --> 01:31:47,982
But in terms of having community transparency to find out on social media that this decision was reversed was so unfortunate.

584
01:31:48,002 --> 01:31:50,063
It was like, oh, it felt like we were moving forward

585
01:31:50,503 --> 01:31:59,065
