587
01:32:16,154 --> 01:32:20,776
that there was going to be some discussion that this might even be the case, you would have had a much larger turnout, I have no doubt.

588
01:32:21,217 --> 01:32:25,859
And people would have felt like they were invested in that decision and had some momentum and part of that decision.

589
01:32:25,959 --> 01:32:40,486
So I guess what I want to ask as we're talking about transparency and moving forward and, you know, hoping that you folks will hear us, and I know that we've done presentations in the past as a CPAC talking about family and community engagement and the need for it.

590
01:32:41,145 --> 01:32:46,606
